Rating: 3
This is very good. The beets need "something" in the end, but I'm not sure what. Very good - I made this with the Parmesan-Dijon Drumsticks and they were fab! The drumsticks need to cook at 350 for 1 hour. The beets need to roast at 450 for 1 hour. I put the drumsticks in with the beets (I have one oven) for 30 minutes together. When the beets were done, I decreased the temperature to 350 and cooked for another 30 minutes. It came out FABULOUS!!!

